CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1967, pg. 24, reads: "Torchlight Picketers - Some of the torchlight-carrying picketing demonstrators who paraded in front of the Callowhill St. home of Meyer and Hilda Talenfeld in the Highland Park District.  A series of at least three demonstrations was staged protesting Talenfelds failure to agree to repair slum housing are shown. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Protesters, including Nate Smith and Reverend Jimmy Joe Robinson, carrying flaming torches and signs protesting against slum landlords outside Talenfeld home, 5640 Callowhill Street, Highland Park
